The history array entries should include a type annotation or interface definition to ensure consistency across the codebase. Currently, the structure is defined inline with no validation. Consider creating an interface like:

interface HistoryEntry {
    event: string;
    timestamp: string;
}

This would provide type safety and make it clear what properties are expected in history entries, especially if different event types need different properties in the future.

