1. `role="button"` attribute to indicate the element is interactive
2. `tabindex="0"` to make it keyboard focusable
3. An appropriate `aria-label` attribute for screen readers
4. Keyboard event handler for Enter and Space keys to trigger the action

Without these attributes, keyboard users and screen reader users cannot access this functionality.
